===Glyph origin 2===
{{zh-forms|alt=𡴀-original,𡵄,𡴇,䒠,仹}}
{{Han etym}}
Originally written {{zh-m|*𡴀}}, {{liushu|p|nocap=1}} of a luxuriant plant growing on the ground {{zh-m|*土}}, which is unrecognizable in the modern version since the bottom stroke is missing. See the top component of {{zh-m|*豐}} and {{zh-m|*奉}}.

Similar but unrelated to {{zh-m|*㞷}} (now {{zh-m|*往}}), {{zh-m|*𤯓}} (now {{zh-m|*生}}), and {{zh-m|*丯}} (now {{zh-m|*㓞}}).

